{"id":310225,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/维权网-上海民众第111次向市人大请愿要求诉权（图/","date":"2013-08-23T14:19:07Z","modified":"2013-08-23T14:19:07Z","title":"维权网 | 上海民众第111次向市人大请愿要求诉权（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员孙小芸报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日</span><span>下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>时，上海</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">83</span><span>名市民陆续到达市人大信访大厅，在维护公民诉权的签名单上签上自己的姓名和电话号码。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>上海市民已经第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">111</span><span>次请求市人大及人大代表履行监督“一府二院”的职责，捍卫法律尊严、维护公民诉权，清除上海司法不作为的恶习。诉权是最基本的人权，诉权得不到维护，更谈不上人权有保障。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>民众推荐赵迪迪、黄尧年、邱贵荣、陈建芳、郑培培五位代表进入人大</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">106</span><span>接待室。接待人员是一位女同志，她不肯告诉姓名，仅报出自己的编号是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">006</span><span>号。市民代表赵迪迪指出：“今天代表中三人是共产党，我有三十年以上党龄，还是一名党支部书记，我们集访人大</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">111</span><span>次了。还是没有解决诉权问题，公民无法立案。立案是法院最基本的工作，不立案必须出具裁定书，这是法院必须走的二条路。如今法院违法，人大长期不管，希望人大走群众路线，改变作风。”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>代表黄尧年指出：“失地农民为了立案已向三级法院请愿</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">373</span><span>天了，问题还是问题，法官不立案闲着无事干，上班玩电脑，下班去嫖娼，法院丑闻不断，院长渎职，司法不作为，上海人大负有不可推卸的责任。”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>邱贵荣指出：“莘庄工业区毁学校，拆教堂、贱卖幼儿园害民扰民十分严重。我有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">40</span><span>年党龄了，向各级部门反映石沉大海，向法院起诉，立案无望。人民对上海党政工作作风、侵害人民利益十分不满。走群众路线，立案无望，法院不如关门，养着法官嫖娼做坏事。”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>陈建芳和郑培培二位代表要求人大负起责任，维护公民诉权，清除司法腐败，保证公民立案是法院最基本起点。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>人大接待室应该是传达人民群众呼声和诉求的窗口，五位代表一致批评上海市人大常委会没有履行职责，导致三级地方法院一再上演剥夺公民诉权的事件发生，造成上海市民严重不满。上海党政言行不一，自毁形象。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">006</span><span>号表示已登记记录会向上反映。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>公民诉权任何人不可侵犯，上海市委和上海人大的领导已十分清楚上海市民诉权被剥夺，但还是装聋作哑。大家希望领导部门要带头走群众路线不搞形式，从解决公民诉权做起，从化解民生问题做起，让上海市民真诚看到上海各级领导走向人民，改变作风。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>位代表离开</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">006</span><span>接待室，与等候在大厅里代表们一起走出市人大信访大门，看到门口有一辆警车和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>多个警察，这些警察在此执行的任务是阻止民众在市人大信访办门口拍集体照。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>民众看到在市人大信访门口拍集体照无望，只好走到人民公园广场拍了第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">111</span><span>次集体照。警察随尾而来又阻止，劝大家回家去。访民孙洪琴责问警察：“我家在哪里？哪里是我的家？我无家可归上你家去好吗？”警察笑而不答。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>参与第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">111</span><span>次“我要立案——维护公民诉权”行动的市民代表有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">83</span><span>人（名单详见附图）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>“我要立案——维护公民诉权”行动请与下述市民代表联系：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>冯正虎（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13524687100</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>焦东海（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13801802454</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>鲁</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">  </span><span>俊（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13651817422</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>赵迪迪（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13482668387</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>朱金娣（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13042111402</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>沈佩兰（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13764885120</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>王扣玛（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13601929155</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>童国菁（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13917920278</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>崔福芳（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13564097383</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>王蓉华（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13162424968</span><span>）</span><span> <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>邱贵荣（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15001903401</span><span>）</span><span> <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>刘洪贤（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13524850369</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>郑培培（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">02153963826</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>孙建敏（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13671947476</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>陈建芳（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15026516445</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>另外，王扣玛被报复陷害仍在狱中受难。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>我要立案网址</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>  </span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://woyaolian.net/\">http://woyaolian.net</a> </span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-FzP0cL_T-f0/UhdjOYR0l5I/AAAAAAAAnNA/YbpxTHdKIDU/s1600/%25E9%259B%2586%25E4%25BD%2593%25E7%2585%25A71.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"206\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-FzP0cL_T-f0/UhdjOYR0l5I/AAAAAAAAnNA/YbpxTHdKIDU/s320/%25E9%259B%2586%25E4%25BD%2593%25E7%2585%25A71.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-2pvve3oP2GU/UhdjRlSPh2I/AAAAAAAAnNM/vStpoh2EtD0/s1600/%E9%9B%86%E4%BD%93%E7%85%A72.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-2pvve3oP2GU/UhdjRlSPh2I/AAAAAAAAnNM/vStpoh2EtD0/s1600/%E9%9B%86%E4%BD%93%E7%85%A72.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Gy4uRLiupu0/UhdjUSAX1BI/AAAAAAAAnNc/Jq53RLcRV6M